title: Corel VideoStudio Ultimate 2018 21.3.0.141 + Content Packs[BabuP
description:
Corel VideoStudio Ultimate just got more creative — and so can you. New VideoStudio Ultimate 2018 brings the intuitive editing experience you

love and turns up the creativity with exciting new features like the Split Screen Video, 3D Title Editor, new premium video effects and more!

Must-haves only in VideoStudio Ultimate 2018:
– NEW Controls and simplified video editing tools
– NEW Split Screen video templates and template creator
– NEW 3D Title Editor and 3D motion titles
– NEW Lens Correction Tools
– NEW Premium Effects from NewBlueFX

New in VideoStudio Ultimate 2018:

Video Editing Shortcuts
We’ve enhanced the tools you use most often! Easily crop, resize, and position your media directly in the preview pane. Snap your media in place with new Smart Guide alignment tools. The entire toolkit is faster and easier to access.

Split Screen Video
Show multiple video streams simultaneously with new Split Screen video templates. Easily drag and drop to create impressive promotional videos or share the highlights from your latest trip!

Ultimate Effects Collection
Tap into hundreds of pro-quality presets and creative effects that deliver results beyond what you thought possible, and give you more time to focus on what matters – your story. Now includes NewBlue Titler Pro 5!

It’s our best VideoStudio yet
Here are just a few of the new features and enhancements in both VideoStudio Pro and Ultimate 2018
